&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Financing as a System &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure financing and capital deployment are embedded into the technology platform&lt;/li&gt;
