&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Development:&lt;/strong&gt; Build and develop your own client portfolio by identifying and acquiring new business opportunities within the assigned market. Build and maintain strong client relationships to foster long-term partnerships.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Market &amp;amp; Strategy:&lt;/strong&gt; Track market trends, pricing, and demand across various regions. You’ll run competitive analyses, identify trading opportunities, and contribute to our buying and selling strategies with real-time insights.&lt;/p&gt;
