&lt;p&gt;To support this evolution, we are launching a new buyout fund with c. €200m in equity and are looking for an &lt;strong&gt;Investment Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to become part of the inaugural team led by two experienced Private Equity Partners - &lt;strong&gt;entrepreneurial,&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;based in Berlin and part of a vibrant tech investing platform&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
