&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;j82ozp&quot; data-start=&quot;863&quot; data-end=&quot;972&quot;&gt;Own the onboarding process end-to-end, from new hire paperwork and equipment setup to first-week schedules.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;edw5hs&quot; data-start=&quot;973&quot; data-end=&quot;1114&quot;&gt;Make sure every new employee feels welcomed and set up for success from day one, and continuously improve the experience based on feedback.&lt;/li&gt;
